-- Canada’s Ivey Index of Purchasing Managers Was 55.3 in June
-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2013-07-05T14:00:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-05/canada-s-ivey-index-of-purchasing-managers-was-55-3-in-june.html
Canada’s Ivey purchasing managers’
index was 55.3 in June on a seasonally adjusted basis, following
a May reading of 63.1, according to a statement on the website
of Western University’s business school.  Readings of more than 50 indicate purchasing by governments
and companies advanced.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Greg Quinn in Ottawa at 
